Ukrainian forces take over Debaltseve, Shakhtarsk, Torez, Lutuhyne, fighting for Pervomaisk and Snizhne underway - Jul. 28, 2014
Ukrainian government troops also entered Shakhtarsk and Torez in Donetsk region and Lutuhyne in Luhansk region. The fighting is currently underway for the complete liberation of Pervomaisk in Luhansk region and Snizhne in Donetsk region.
In addition, Ukrainian Armed Forces and National Guard units deployed on the outskirts of Horlivka in Donetsk region and are preparing to liberate it, reads the report.